config GPU_POWER_MGMT
	tristate "GPU Power Profile Management"
	depends on PM
	help
	  This enables the GPU power profile management system that provides
	  optimized profiles for different use cases:
	  
	  - Power Save: Optimized for battery life
	  - Balanced: Normal performance
	  - High Performance: Maximum performance with AI optimization
	  
	  The system includes automatic AI-based performance tuning in
	  high performance mode for optimal gaming and video editing
	  performance while managing thermals and power consumption.
	  
	  If unsure, say N.
